{{Top|leg}}
A '''cargo lifter''', '''cargo speeder''', or '''sky lorry''' was any utility airship used in [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceports]] in the loading and unloading of cargo. Older cargo lifters used mechanical claws for handling cargo while newer models use [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsors]] and [[Tractor beam/Legends|tractor beams]].

Cargo lifters were classed as a type of [[Remote/Legends|remote]].<ref name="EGWT">''[[The Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref>

